          Total timeline from starting work to PR landing:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>9 months:</strong> Work experience requirement</li>
          <li><strong>1-6 months:</strong> Wait for invitation (varies by draw frequency)</li>
          <li><strong>3-4 months:</strong> BC PNP processing</li>
          <li><strong>15-21 months:</strong> Federal PR processing (non-Express Entry)</li>
          <li><strong>Total:</strong> Approximately 28-40 months</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Can I work multiple jobs to reach 30 hours/week?</h3>
        <p>
          Yes, but only if both jobs are with the <em>same employer</em>. Working part-time for two different employers does not qualify as full-time work for ELSS purposes.
        </p>

